    "The UpSet plot between the learning tasks.",
    "Medical DSS, Medical Decision Support System; E.F., emotion or face; P.M.L.N., psychiatric, mood, learning, or neurodevelopmental; E.G.A, Experience, Gender, or Age Categorization.",
    "and Healthcare are closely related.",
    "We assigned a publication to Healthcare if it focused on diagnosis only.",
    "If the underlying visual behavior was investigated as well, such as in Hayes and Henderson (2018), we assigned both domains."
